    <h3 class="cag-h3">The Three Numbers That Surprised Us</h3>
    <p>On 2026-07-12 we ran a reproducible sweep of thirty African Grey breeder and listing sites — a homepage keyword scan plus a sitemap probe, the script and results saved for anyone to re-run.</p>
