    <h3 class="cag-h3">Nationwide Shipping and Two Delivery Tiers</h3>
    <p>The full African Grey shipping process — crate standards, timing and what arrival day looks like — has its own page. Wherever the bird lands, the CITES, DNA, PCR and vet paperwork travels with it. Tap a route to see that area's availability:</p>
