    <h3 class="cag-h3">A Family Aviary in Midland, Texas Since 2014</h3>
    <figure class="pullquote">
      <blockquote>"We wrote this comparison the way we answer the phone — if the paperwork does not check out, we would rather you walk away, even from us. A documented bird is the only kind worth a forty-year commitment."</blockquote>
      <figcaption>
        <img class="q-av" src="/roys-congo-african-grey-male-tame-card.webp" width="56" height="56" alt="A hand-raised African Grey at the C.A.Gs aviary in Midland, TX" loading="lazy">
        <span class="pq-id"><b>Mark &amp; Teri Benjamin</b> · C.A.Gs, Midland, TX</span>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <p>Mark and Teri have hand-raised African Greys in Midland since 2014, and answered the "how do I know you are legit?" question for nearly as long. The full story, credentials and USDA framing live on our <a href="/trusted-african-grey-parrot-breeders/">about the breeders page</a> — the same standard of proof this comparison asks of every seller.</p>
