    <p>If a sale went wrong, report it in three places and save every message first. <a href="https://www.ic3.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IC3.gov, the FBI's Internet Crime Complaint Center ↗</a>, handles online fraud; <a href="https://aphis.usda.gov/aphis/ourfocus/animalwelfare" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the USDA APHIS Animal Care program ↗</a> takes CITES and welfare concerns; and your state attorney general's consumer-protection office handles the financial side. Then call your card issuer or PayPal to open a dispute.</p>
